---
title: Spiced Moroccan Lentil and Chickpea Soup with Sour Cream and Toasted Pita
description: Ras-El-Hanout is a spice blend common in North African cuisine, and features heavily in Moroccan cuisine. Blends can be slightly different depending on region and can contain anywhere from 10 to 100 different spices! This spice is what makes this soup so flavourful and aromatic!
